 "html": "<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5833 size-large\" src=\"/media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9012-1024x768.jpg\" alt width=\"530\" height=\"398\" srcset=\"/media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9012-1024x768.jpg 1024w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9012-600x450.jpg 600w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9012-300x225.jpg 300w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9012-768x576.jpg 768w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9012-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9012-750x563.jpg 750w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9012-500x375.jpg 500w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9012-380x285.jpg 380w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9012-760x570.jpg 760w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9012-800x600.jpg 800w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9012.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 530px) 100vw, 530px\"></p>\n<p>My ma het baie keer op &#8216;n Saterdag vir ons souttert gemaak.    Dit was voor die dae van quiche.  Jy kan die worsies vervang met Bullybeef as jy daarna voel.  My ma het blikkies viennas gebruik &#8211; dit is ook reg.</p>\n<h3>Bestanddele</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>3 eiers</li>\n<li>375 ml melk</li>\n<li>30 ml koekmeel</li>\n<li>6 weenseworsies of 1 blikkie weenseworsies in ringetjies gesny</li>\n<li>200 g baconstukkies</li>\n<li>250 ml gerasperde kaas</li>\n<li>1 ui gerasper</li>\n<li>10 ml mostertpoeier</li>\n<li>sout en peper</li>\n<li>100 ml fyngekapte pietersielie</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5831 size-medium\" src=\"/media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9019-300x225.jpg\" alt width=\"300\" height=\"225\" srcset=\"/media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9019-300x225.jpg 300w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9019-600x450.jpg 600w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9019-1024x768.jpg 1024w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9019-768x576.jpg 768w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9019-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9019-750x563.jpg 750w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9019-500x375.jpg 500w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9019-380x285.jpg 380w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9019-760x570.jpg 760w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9019-800x600.jpg 800w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9019.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\"></p>\n<h3>Metode</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Braai die ui en bacon in botter.</li>\n<li>Gooi die weenseworsies by en braai so bietjie en  laat dit afkoel</li>\n<li>Klits die eiers en melk met &#8216;n ballonklitser.</li>\n<li>Klits die meel en mostertpoeier by.</li>\n<li>Roer die kaas in.</li>\n<li>Roer die uie/bacon en worsiemengsel by die eiermengsel.</li>\n<li>As jy bacon gebruik wees versigtig met sout, want die bacon is baie sout.  Andersins sout en peper na smaak.</li>\n<li>Roer die fyngekapte pietersielie in.</li>\n<li>Gooi in &#8216;n gesmeerde bak en sit in die oond teen 180C vir 30 &#8211; 40 minute.</li>\n<li>Die tert kan koud of warm geeet word.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-5832 size-large\" src=\"/media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9025-2-1024x782.jpg\" alt width=\"530\" height=\"405\" srcset=\"/media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9025-2-1024x782.jpg 1024w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9025-2-600x458.jpg 600w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9025-2-300x229.jpg 300w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9025-2-768x587.jpg 768w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9025-2-1536x1173.jpg 1536w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9025-2-750x573.jpg 750w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9025-2-380x290.jpg 380w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9025-2-760x580.jpg 760w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9025-2-800x611.jpg 800w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9025-2-90x70.jpg 90w, /media/uploads/2020/05/IMG_9025-2.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 530px) 100vw, 530px\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
